Assignment 02:
	Complete the following three tasks:
	1. Create a file with some data (about 3 to 5 sentences per line) and copy it to a hdfs
	location of your choice
	2. Write a MapReduce program to count the number of lines in the file created in the
	previous task (task 1 of this assignment)
	3. Write a MapReduce program to remove the records for which the length of the record is
	less than 15
